{"tid":1754843,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"美玩討論區（27）建制派大敗","createTime":"2019-11-25T10:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T10:16:56.000Z","uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a47fc763a990ced675e27664363812c50fbaed6b","tid":1754843,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"今場仗嘅勝利係好多手足犧牲換返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n場仗仲未完<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n玩具去邊買<br />\n孩記既Marvel Legends /Black Series邊到訂/買?<br />\n1)信和 Hobbybase/現時點/灣仔玩具街<br />\n2)再唔係amazon/旋轉app買<br />\n3)奇趣天地/Toyrus/孤注一扭<br />\n4)銅鑼灣糖街 美漫店 Metro 同Clark's Comics<br />\n5)柴灣 Ht toyshop<br />\n<br />\nShf Mafex邊到買?<br />\n1)信和/現時點/兆萬<br />\n2)再唔係大鋪肥趣/百貨 不過貴<br />\n3)aimami <a href=\"http://www.amiami.com/top/page/c/character_figure.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.amiami.com%2Ftop%2Fpage%2Fc%2Fcharacter_figure.html&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=605bb56d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.amiami.com/top/page/c/character_figure.html</a><br />\n<br />\n老翻list（歡迎大家update個list<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nShf marvel : Tony , black widow ,black panther,captain ,homecoming Spider-Man ,homemade suit Spider-Man ,cw antman,hulk,Ironman mk43+sofa ,iw starlord, iw iron spider<br />\n<br />\nShf DC:the joker, batman<br />\n<br />\nShf star wars:ep4 luke, ep6 luke,clone trooper <br />\n<br />\nMafex:Batman,the joker,bvs Batman，Wonder Woman ,amazing Spider-Man,homecoming Spider-Man <br />\n<br />\n山口式：deadpool,漫畫captain,漫畫Spider-Man,漫畫毒液，漫畫磁力王<br />\n<br />\nMezco:bvs Batman,bvs Superman,deadpool,captain,罰叔<br />\n<br />\nPs:以上係小弟記憶中見過既流野，盡量唔好買呢d既二手免貍貓換太子 雖然有d qc一睇就知假<br />\n<br />\n其他<br />\nBall joint關節太鬆:<br />\n1.)用AA膠滴幾點係個球波度 用來增加厚度<br />\n2.)完全乾透先入裝返上去<br />\n3.)仲鬆就重複1,2 直到緊為止 / 關節實過頭 沙紙磨一磨,唔一定AA膠,不過普遍多人用...指甲油都有人會用"},{"pid":"a6515bd78cd3f862b5834698ef92fa2a47db9131","tid":1754843,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑店：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yR3WZQ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyR3WZQ5.png&h=31cc4007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-出貨遲幾個月 <br />\n比街貨遲3個月 次次問都話下個禮拜<br />\n下個禮拜又係冇 <br />\n<br />\n-道德綁架客人<br />\n用關心香港黎迫人認同遲出貨合理<br />\n<br />\n-因為d貨蟹左 唔俾人退訂<br />\n蜘蛛俠set冇跌價 所以退訂<br />\n<br />\n-洩漏客人資料"},{"pid":"dff428006e88b9bae1f421f06d336ea910f54a15","tid":1754843,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"搵左好耐真係搵唔到任何關於 PCToys 呢間廠既資料. 唔知其他人係點contact到間公司羅貨. 1/12 無人機佢好似高汁過Boring Toys唔少, 但香港訂價同淘寶見到既基本上一樣價, 即係大陸今次食水好深[/quote]$130嘅話又真係幾抵，唔知係香港定大陸呢[/quote]最驚俾咗錢收唔到貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]唔駛驚，向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新垣潔衣寶寶</strong></span>拜師學藝，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>會員編號: #3549</strong></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>FB: Yip Chunyin</strong></span>，佢好叻屈9商鋪退訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWKvqOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWKvqOR.jpg&h=ef8c4eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rvjji8R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvjji8R.jpg&h=56ccebaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86f1aa28127a3c65623502b8591e1c1c1a916ba6","tid":1754843,"uid":24532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfbGzka.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfbGzka.jpg&h=204b5169&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdYByw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F